PrecisAppointment of an ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of ALBERTA, namely the Hon. RENE PAUL FOISY, who shall execute the office and functions of the Lieutenant Governor from July 28 to August 14, 1995, during the absence, illness or other inability of the latter.
